Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:48.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:56.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}风沙遮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:02:03.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}无论何时 都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}日常之事 不曾改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:16.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}看一看吧 那充满光芒的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:21.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}永远永远都在守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:25.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望着朵朵流逝的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:32.86,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感受着变化无穷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}驻足而立的我们察觉到
